---
pageable: false
per_page: 1
---

- page_articles.select { |item| item.metadata[:page]["featured"]}.each_with_index do |article, i|
  %p Featured content only with special design
  %h2= article.data.title
  %p= summary(article)
  %p
    %small= article.date.strftime('%Y, %b %e ')
  %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-read{:href => article.url} Read More